| comment "Dragnet [Ransomware]: dragnet-ransomware-2024-5464 — Recovery Inhibition (cloak)"
| comment "Status: experimental | Level: high | ID: c9e4630b-ded4-57d3-9f1b-bee3b6df7ea2"
